{"tid":553804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雞扒妹會面神之手加藤鷹 評D奶「夠大了」","createTime":"2018-02-08T00:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T18:33:04.000Z","uid":25345,"like":238,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"f899584da0d8f559c17aec9ddbb2677a5f591746","tid":553804,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T00:41:12.000Z","msg":"藝人雞排妹今趕回台灣與加藤鷹一起參加《抓GO樂》遊戲記者會，雞排妹說日本大雪，所以有此軟體很方便，加藤鷹則說不怕娃娃難夾，因他手指靈活沒問題。 雞排妹說在日北太冷就不會出門，加藤鷹則說喝酒後最愛去夾娃娃！享受夾到的樂趣跟成果。<br />\n<br />\n而被問到在日本的情況，雞排妹說現在就是念語言學校，在兩個月才會再回台，情人節也是自己過，不過她透露有奇怪豔遇，「我跟我朋友在六本木附近街上走，結果有3個日本男人看起來就是喝過酒的，就過來問我要不要一起去喝一杯，我一直說不要，他們還是糾纏我，最後是賣沙威瑪的中東朋友幫我解圍，我也邀他們去警局他們才罷休」。<br />\n<br />\n雞排妹跟加藤鷹也被媒體問到合作的可能，加藤鷹表示：「其實雞排妹在現在的領域上工作就很好了，不是每個人都適合去拍ＡＶ。」此時雞排妹心虛地說，最近瘦3公斤（44公斤，156公分），胸部這麼小（現在是30D）可以嗎？加藤鷹笑說，「完全沒問題，夠大了」。<br />\n<br />\n兩人在現場也被問看到花蓮強震的心情，雞排妹說，昨天有被小驚嚇，加藤鷹說：「昨晚住在11樓真的很晃，一想到日本311大地震台灣人給予日本那麼多幫助與捐款，真的很感動，我跟雞排妹都應該為災區加油！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180207/640_95476bf8acedc14c121a22c2747c88eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180207%2F640_95476bf8acedc14c121a22c2747c88eb.jpg&h=f53bef09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180207/640_e41aea652412ec751ba9f4ff62d689c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180207%2F640_e41aea652412ec751ba9f4ff62d689c2.jpg&h=134a94b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180207/640_497baa4f8821e68f8a48d48c2eee878b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180207%2F640_497baa4f8821e68f8a48d48c2eee878b.jpg&h=04a48ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180207/640_4fb03f4c3186d7661b92dda9277cb06b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180207%2F640_4fb03f4c3186d7661b92dda9277cb06b.jpg&h=7211eb8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180207/640_be113cc67d7e5218592f5e90b3810905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180207%2F640_be113cc67d7e5218592f5e90b3810905.jpg&h=72bb0863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/27657719_1446529608803251_7570708965912473221_n.jpg?oh=22b1be72206a881a1d9319a9a5916a20&amp;oe=5B18BC32\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F27657719_1446529608803251_7570708965912473221_n.jpg%3Foh%3D22b1be72206a881a1d9319a9a5916a20%26oe%3D5B18BC32&h=2794526f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dca18abc0e4855aa459268a852dc8b92670bb54","tid":553804,"uid":85099,"like":317,"dislike":9,"score":308,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T00:43:30.000Z","msg":"好想舔佢對奶"},{"pid":"e719c0a807af59298498d9e0cea772fbc0899ed2","tid":553804,"uid":60655,"like":148,"dislike":2,"score":146,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T00:47:31.000Z","msg":"佢對波縮左水"},{"pid":"af869dc022bf858f0bd1820412825ac12ef770cd","tid":553804,"uid":16777,"like":195,"dislike":4,"score":191,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T00:50:54.000Z","msg":"最正係個雞屎忽"},{"pid":"fe336fdbc544aea0348cd9a78e57232317d20bc4","tid":553804,"uid":52358,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T00:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca03c00e0100f68c9cac72ef4a709bddabeb3cff","tid":553804,"uid":37735,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T00:53:28.000Z","msg":"夜晚有下場?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6c77be9a99037ba3c33a92ee89a0c08e95d653","tid":553804,"uid":44858,"like":30,"dislike":9,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T00:54:57.000Z","msg":"咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯咯"},{"pi