e":"2018-02-08T12:05:38.000Z","msg":"有冇聽過性交轉運呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLin燈真係多小學豬"},{"pid":"1fee06be83a293525e04b2e22f8b0e097bc98c66","tid":553804,"uid":69994,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:06:41.000Z","msg":"有特殊需要 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">發表日期：2014/09/11<br />\n<br />\n久前才嗆跟前男友溫晉禾「復合就下地獄」的雞排妹，上週竟被本刊直擊又睡進前男友家，待了21小時後，才穿著同一套小洋裝，然後腳開開地坐著前男友騎的機車離開；糾纏9個月、2度分合的「雞溫戀」正式往地獄蔓延。<br />\n<br />\n上月底，雞排妹（鄭家純）才自爆跟揍過她的前男友溫晉禾二度分手，當時她為了強調不是炒作，還發毒誓「復合就下地獄」；沒想到話才講沒多久，二十一歲的她已經偷偷走上了地獄之路。</div>"},{"pid":"feb2fe99af5b1210a00102c0c1c37819ec7d2df4","tid":553804,"uid":24935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"做男優做到咁幾堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人知當年同佢齊名既朱古力波而家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f800d1a6fd083b85dd0e7b698bee89dec35be8b5","tid":553804,"uid":60763,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:07:22.000Z","msg":"大師都話夠大<br />\n咪夠大囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ca01269bcfc3ad110f89af069fca6661d46ec5","tid":553804,"uid":41130,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"f800d1a6fd083b85dd0e7b698bee89dec35be8b5","tid":553804,"uid":60763,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:07:22.000Z","msg":"大師都話夠大<br />\n咪夠大囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"連登仔話細就細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁都叫大?<br />\n加藤鷹肯定係青頭毒撚"},{"pid":"39dcda1d751ea1177ea495de465f6ed1c6f0767e","tid":553804,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T12:09:02.000Z","msg